Games::Perlwar version 0.03
===========

===== INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl ./Build.PL
   ./Build
   ./Build test
   ./Build install

   or, if you are old-school,

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

===== WEB ENVIROMENT

To run PerlWar's web environment, you'll need an Apache 
server and the following modules:

    * AxKit
    * XML::XPathScript
    * Embperl

Copy the directory 'web' included in the distribution as 'perlwar' 
at the document root of Apache. E.g.:

    cp -R web /home/web/htdocs/perlwar

Games must be created as sub-directories of this directory. Don't
forget to change the permission of the game directories so that
they are writable by the Apache user. 
